                <mxCell id="dep_notes" value="&lt;b&gt;Deployment considerations:&lt;/b&gt; Azure Workload Identity per namespace · Network policy: workers → adapters (allow), workers ↔ internet (deny) · mTLS via Envoy · Skill hot-reload over gRPC stream · Knowledge store TTL staleness guard · All tool calls audited to ADX · Node pools: system + worker + (optional) gpu" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;fillColor=#F4F6FB;strokeColor=#8A94A6;fontSize=11;fontColor=#3D4663;strokeWidth=0.5;" parent="1" vertex="1">
